145
00:06:18,319 --> 00:06:19,240
Are you okay, Nian?

146
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,519
I'm fine. Are you okay?

147
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:25,040
Yes, I'm fine. I'll take you home.

148
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,399
Going home?

149
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,920
Dong is home alone.

150
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,399
Qiufen?

